NHL ALL-STAR WEEKEND
February 6, 2000
Pavol Demitra
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   
 Q. What is it like to be in the All-Star game?
 
 PAVOL DEMITRA: I am just happy to be here. Just with all the great hockey players here,
a bunch of great guys. To see all the guys it is very exciting for me. 
 
Q. You played a little while in Ottawa, but the reception here in Toronto, what does
that lead you to believe about this city and hockey in the country?
 
 PAVOL DEMITRA: Like I never see something like that. This is a great city for hockey
and they did a great job and everybody is so excited. 
 
Q. Congratulations.
